      "content": "i tried the water but im still kinda trippy and my speech is still all over the place. it's hard for me to even type this right lol. i dont really wanna go to the hospital if i can help it because the wait times here are crazy. can i just take some extra electrolytes and maybe some aspirin to help with the head feeling? would that fix it?",
